      "updated": 1772480207001,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "On page load popup.ts loads the\nUI/UX for the extension's popup,\nadd a listener to the button for\nstarting the video anaylsis. If that\nbutton is clicked then sends a\nmessage to the contentScript.ts\nworker",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "On page load popup.ts loads the UI/UX for the extension's popup, add a listener to the button for starting the video anaylsis. If that button is clicked then sends a message to the contentScript.ts worker",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "u1aSQs4kqaFrn8a_wgEnt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 84.3591029299007,
      "y": -794.3867212000978,
      "width": 262.6582141987601,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ai",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2033643290,
      "version": 402,
      "versionNonce": 189772998,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772480280141,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When the contentScript.ts\nreceives the message, it\nscrapes for the transcript,\nchannel name, video title,\nand video id. Once it\nreceives this it sends a\nmessage out to the\nbackground.ts worker with\nthe information",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When the contentScript.ts receives the message, it scrapes for the transcript, channel name, video title, and video id. Once it receives this it sends a message out to the background.ts worker with the information",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZRSU8btLxPxrxPhN4eW6t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 434.83732865340664,
      "y": -796.3604117543464,
      "width": 445.296912287622,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aj",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 367985690,
      "version": 603,
      "versionNonce": 2067742426,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772480386446,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When the background worker receives the\nmessage, it begin analysis of the information\nusing a model running on the user's GPU that\nscores the video. When it's done it saves the\nscore to the browser's storage (it may have\nto send a message to the contentScript.ts\nworker, other it'll do it itself). Then once it's\nsaved a message will be sent out for the\npop.ts",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When the background worker receives the message, it begin analysis of the information using a model running on the user's GPU that scores the video. When it's done it saves the score to the browser's storage (it may have to send a message to the contentScript.ts worker, other it'll do it itself). Then once it's saved a message will be sent out for the pop.ts",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "qD1LdWm4AaKbNg6bHjZM8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 973.6598720766069,
      "y": -747.8417744907471,
      "width": 428.17642379801765,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ak",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1265582470,
      "version": 306,
      "versionNonce": 1982983130,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772480425522,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Once the popup.ts receives the message\nthat the video has been scored, it will\nfetch for the video id from storage and\npresent the result to the user",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Once the popup.ts receives the message that the video has been scored, it will fetch for the video id from storage and present the result to the user",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
